        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEMA Loan Interest Payment Relief Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill directs the Federal Emergency Management Agency (FEMA) to provide financial assistance to a local government or electric cooperative as reimbursement for qualifying interest on disaster-related loans.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
